            "is_bold": false,
            "text": "Control:  Retain audit records for [Assignment: organization-defined time period consistent with records retention policy] to provide support for after-the-fact investigations of incidents and to meet regulatory and organizational information retention requirements."
          },
          "source_type": "Body",
